---
import PageLayout from '@/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout
  title="Terms of Service | Figgle Media"
  description="Read Figgle Media's terms of service. These terms govern your use of our website and services."
  heroTitle="Terms of Service"
  heroSubtitle="Last updated: January 2026"
  breadcrumbs={[
    { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
    { label: 'Terms of Service' }
  ]}
>
  <section class="legal-content">
    <div class="container container-narrow">
      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Agreement to Terms</h2>
        <p>By accessing or using Figgle Media's website and services, you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service. If you disagree with any part of these terms, you may not access our services.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Services</h2>
        <p>Figgle Media provides digital marketing services including but not limited to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Search Engine Optimization (SEO)</li>
          <li>Website Design and Development</li>
          <li>Social Media Marketing</li>
          <li>Pay-Per-Click Advertising Management</li>
          <li>Content Marketing</li>
        </ul>
        <p>The specific services provided will be outlined in your service agreement or proposal.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Payment Terms</h2>
        <p>Services are billed monthly in advance unless otherwise specified in your service agreement. Payment is due upon receipt of invoice. We accept major credit cards, ACH transfers, and checks.</p>
        <p>Late payments may result in suspension of services after a 10-day grace period and written notice.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Cancellation Policy</h2>
        <p>You may cancel your services at any time with 30 days written notice. Upon cancellation:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>All work completed will be delivered to you</li>
          <li>Access credentials for all accounts will be transferred</li>
          <li>Any outstanding invoices become due immediately</li>
          <li>No refunds are provided for partial months</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p>Upon full payment, you own all deliverables created specifically for your business, including:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Website designs and code</li>
          <li>Written content and copy</li>
          <li>Graphics and images created for your brand</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Figgle Media retains the right to showcase work in our portfolio unless otherwise agreed in writing.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Client Responsibilities</h2>
        <p>You agree to:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Provide timely feedback and approvals</li>
          <li>Supply accurate information about your business</li>
          <li>Maintain current contact information</li>
          <li>Respond to requests within reasonable timeframes</li>
          <li>Comply with all applicable laws regarding your business and advertising</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
        <p>Figgle Media shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, consequential, or punitive damages resulting from your use of our services. Our total liability shall not exceed the amount paid for services in the three months preceding the claim.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>No Guarantees</h2>
        <p>While we strive for the best possible results, we cannot guarantee specific outcomes such as:</p>
        <ul>
          <li>Specific search engine rankings</li>
          <li>Specific traffic or lead volumes</li>
          <li>Specific return on investment</li>
        </ul>
        <p>Search engine algorithms and market conditions are outside our control. We commit to following industry best practices and being transparent about our efforts and results.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Modifications to Terms</h2>
        <p>We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time. We will notify you of significant changes via email or through our website. Continued use of our services after changes constitutes acceptance of the new terms.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Governing Law</h2>
        <p>These terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the State of North Carolina, without regard to its conflict of law provisions.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="legal-section">
        <h2>Contact Information</h2>
        <p>For questions about these Terms of Service, please contact us:</p>
        <p>
          <strong>Email:</strong> Figglemedia@gmail.com<br>
          <strong>Phone:</strong> (681) 307-7514
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .legal-content {
    padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
    background: var(--color-bg-main);
  }

  .container-narrow {
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .legal-section {
    margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
  }

  .legal-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    color: var(--color-cream);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--color-accent-primary);
  }

  .legal-section p {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    line-height: 1.8;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .legal-section ul {
    color: var(--color-text-light);
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
  }

  .legal-section li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
</style>
